test

Test-cases:

ID: 1
Title: User's authorization at website "Учет запчастей"
Pre-conditions:
1. Open http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com
Steps:
1. Enter valid login in 'Login' field (Student)
2. Enter valid password in "Password" field (909090)
3. Click on [Вход]
Expected result:
User should be navigated to Main page with user avatar

ID:2
Title:  Adding new deal at site "Учет запчастей"
Pre-conditions:
1. Open http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com
2. Enter valid login in 'Login' field (Student)
3. Enter valid password in "Password" field (909090)
4. Click on [Вход]
Steps:
1. At sidebar menu click on "Сделки" option
2. Click on [+] in right upper corner
3. Set 'Deal Date'
4. Select 'Deal Type'
5. Set Сustomer name in "Покупатель" field
6. Set Provider name in "Поставщик" field
7. Click on [Создать]
Expected result:
Newly created deal should be displayed in the bottom of Deals list

ID:3
Title: Creating new type of deal
Pre-conditions:
1. Open http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com
2. Enter valid login in 'Login' field (Student)
3. Enter valid password in "Password" field (909090)
4. Click on [Вход]
Steps:
1. In sidebar menu click on option "Словари"
2. In drop-down list click on item "Типы сделок"
3. Сlick on [+] in right upper corner
4. Enter name for deal type into "Deal type name" field
5. Click on [Создать]

Expected result:
Newly created deal type should be displayed at the end of Deal Types List

ID: 4
Title: Adding new worker to Workers List
Pre-conditions:
1. Open http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com
2. Enter valid login in 'Login' field (Student)
3. Enter valid password in "Password" field (909090)
4. Click on [Вход]

Steps:
1. In sidebar menu click on option "Словари"
2. In drop-down list click on item "Сотрудники"
3. Сlick on [+] in the right upper corner
4. Enter worker surname into "Worker surname" field
5. Enter worker name into "Worker name" field
6. Enter worker middle name into "Worker middle name" field
7. Enter worker phone into "Worker phone" field
8. Click on [Cоздать]

Expected result:
New worker should be added to the end of Workers list;
Worker name, surname and middle name should be displayed in 'Сотрудник' column and phone in 'Телефон' column

ID: 5
Title: Logout from user account on site "Учет запчастей"
Pre-conditions:
1. Open http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com
2. Enter valid login in 'Login' field (Student)
3. Enter valid password in "Password" field (909090)
4. Click on [Вход]
Steps:
1. Сlick on user avatar in right upper corner
2. In appeared pop-up click on [Выход]
Expected result:
Authorization page should be opened






